title: Visual Thesaurus 3
description:
Visual Thesaurus 3
No Virus
A remarkably inventive and interactive way to explore language, Visual Thesaurus was one of our favorite products in 2003. Version 3 includes more words (including proper nouns), American and British English audio pronunciations and spellings, fun new display modes, a cool configurable display, content-filtering options, and (online only) searches in French, Spanish, and other languages
